msgctxt "an3.40:2.6"
msgid ""
"Appeva nāma imassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa antakiriyā paññāyethā’ti."
msgstr ""
"And I thought, “Hopefully I can find an end to this entire mass of "
"suffering.”"

msgctxt "an3.40:2.7"
msgid ""
"Ahañceva kho pana evaṃ pabbajito samāno kāmavitakkaṃ vā vitakkeyyaṃ, "
"byāpādavitakkaṃ vā vitakkeyyaṃ, vihiṃsāvitakkaṃ vā vitakkeyyaṃ, mahā kho "
"panāyaṃ lokasannivāso."
msgstr ""
"And now, since I’ve now gone forth, I might have sensual, malicious, or "
"cruel thoughts. But the population of the world is large,"

msgctxt "an3.40:2.8"
msgid ""
"Mahantasmiṃ kho pana lokasannivāse santi samaṇabrāhmaṇā iddhimanto "
"dibbacakkhukā paracittaviduno."
msgstr ""
"and there are ascetics and brahmins who have psychic power—they’re "
"clairvoyant, and can read the minds of others."

#. VAR: pajānanti → jānanti (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an3.40:2.9"
msgid "Te dūratopi passanti, āsannāpi na dissanti, cetasāpi cittaṃ pajānanti."
msgstr ""
"They see far without being seen, even by those close; and they understand "
"the minds of others."

msgctxt "an3.40:2.10"
msgid "Tepi maṃ evaṃ jāneyyuṃ:"
msgstr "They would know me:"

msgctxt "an3.40:2.11"
msgid ""
"‘passatha, bho, imaṃ kulaputtaṃ saddhā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito samāno "
"vokiṇṇo viharati pāpakehi akusalehi dhammehī’ti."
msgstr ""
"“Look at this person from a good family; they’ve gone forth out of faith "
"from the lay life to homelessness, but they’re living mixed up with bad, "
"unskillful qualities.”"

msgctxt "an3.40:2.12"
msgid "devatāpi kho santi iddhimantiniyo dibbacakkhukā paracittaviduniyo."
msgstr ""
"And there are deities, too, who have psychic power—they’re clairvoyant, and "
"can read the minds of others."

msgctxt "an3.40:2.13"
msgid "Tā dūratopi passanti, āsannāpi na dissanti, cetasāpi cittaṃ jānanti."
msgstr ""
"They see far without being seen, even by those close; and they understand "
"the minds of others."

msgctxt "an3.40:2.14"
msgid "Tāpi maṃ evaṃ jāneyyuṃ:"
msgstr "They would know me:"

msgctxt "an3.40:2.15"
msgid ""
"‘passatha, bho, imaṃ kulaputtaṃ saddhā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito samāno "
"vokiṇṇo viharati pāpakehi akusalehi dhammehī’ti."
msgstr ""
"“Look at this person from a good family; they’ve gone forth out of faith "
"from the lay life to homelessness, but they’re living mixed up with bad, "
"unskillful qualities.”"

msgctxt "an3.40:2.16"
msgid "So iti paṭisañcikkhati:"
msgstr "Then they reflect:"

msgctxt "an3.40:2.17"
msgid ""
"‘āraddhaṃ kho pana me vīriyaṃ bhavissati asallīnaṃ, upaṭṭhitā sati "
"asammuṭṭhā, passaddho kāyo asāraddho, samāhitaṃ cittaṃ ekaggan’ti."
msgstr ""
