"established and lucid, my body shall be tranquil and undisturbed, and my "
"mind shall be immersed in samādhi.’"

msgctxt "an3.40:2.18"
msgid ""
"So lokaṃyeva adhipatiṃ karitvā akusalaṃ pajahati, kusalaṃ bhāveti, sāvajjaṃ "
"pajahati, anavajjaṃ bhāveti, suddhaṃ attānaṃ pariharati."
msgstr ""
"Putting the world in charge, they give up the unskillful and develop the "
"skillful, they give up the blameworthy and develop the blameless, and they "
"keep themselves pure."

msgctxt "an3.40:2.19"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, lokādhipateyyaṃ."
msgstr "This is called putting the world in charge."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.40:3.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dhammādhipateyyaṃ?"
msgstr "And what, mendicants, is putting the teaching in charge?"

msgctxt "an3.40:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu araññagato vā rukkhamūlagato vā suññāgāragato vā "
"iti paṭisañcikkhati:"
msgstr ""
