msgid "Appeva nāma imassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa antakiriyā paññāyethāti."
msgstr ""
"And I thought, “Hopefully I can find an end to this entire mass of "
"suffering.”"

msgctxt "an3.40:3.7"
msgid ""
"Svākkhāto bhagavatā dhammo sandiṭṭhiko akāliko ehipassiko opaneyyiko "
"paccattaṃ veditabbo viññūhīti."
msgstr ""
"The teaching is well explained by the Buddha—realizable in this very life, "
"immediately effective, inviting inspection, relevant, so that sensible "
"people can know it for themselves."

msgctxt "an3.40:3.8"
msgid "Santi kho pana me sabrahmacārī jānaṃ passaṃ viharanti."
msgstr "I have spiritual companions who live knowing and seeing."

msgctxt "an3.40:3.9"
msgid ""
"Ahañceva kho pana evaṃ svākkhāte dhammavinaye pabbajito samāno kusīto "
"vihareyyaṃ pamatto, na metaṃ assa patirūpan’ti."
msgstr ""
"Now that I’ve gone forth in this well explained teaching and training, it "
"would not be appropriate for me to live lazy and heedless.’"

msgctxt "an3.40:3.10"
msgid "So iti paṭisañcikkhati:"
msgstr "Then they reflect:"

msgctxt "an3.40:3.11"
msgid ""
"‘āraddhaṃ kho pana me vīriyaṃ bhavissati asallīnaṃ, upaṭṭhitā sati "
"asammuṭṭhā, passaddho kāyo asāraddho, samāhitaṃ cittaṃ ekaggan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘My energy shall be roused up and unflagging, mindfulness shall be "
"established and lucid, my body shall be tranquil and undisturbed, and my "
"mind shall be immersed in samādhi.’"

msgctxt "an3.40:3.12"
msgid ""
